Hello,

this is the second version of my jail map.

Features of this map:

Climb
Minigame
Football/Soccer
Swimminghall
healroom
some ways to escape for the T's

Recommed maximal 32 Persons. 24 Terrorists and 8 Counter Terrorists.

There will be some new Versions of this map and new features in the feature.

If there are bugs or if you have some suggestions, please contact me.
